{"tid":763744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟人守規矩係好事定壞事？","createTime":"2018-08-01T11:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T13:18:56.000Z","uid":64694,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"66473d846a4fff284a369697edc068229631afe4","tid":763744,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"以前小學中學甚至父母都叫我哋守規矩，所以我由細到大都扮一個乖乖仔咁，唔會對任何嘢作出反抗對抗，循規蹈矩，老師都會好鍾意我，操行通常都畀A我，但其實一直扮住乖乖仔嘅性格有時都會覺得好辛苦，唔知係咪因為人嘅性格有時係想break the rules<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以最近我喺度諗，到底永遠跟住社會規則嚟行，唔犯錯唔犯規，係咪真係一件好事嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人話女人鍾意啲壞壞哋嘅男仔，男人唔壞女人唔愛，如果個人平時太過鍾意遵守規則，女人係咪真係唔會鍾意呢類嘅男仔呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有就係，我覺得如果啲規則太多又嚴格嘅話，好似新加坡咁，遵守晒呢啲規則雖然可能會令到個社會安定啲，但係班人變得太乖係咪真係好事呢？有個感覺就係個個變到好似一班機械人咁，有少少行屍走肉嘅感覺咁<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家又點睇呢？<br />\n<br />\n講講吓好似守護蛋精靈咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7d2a2087d097774a8b106b2d11fe3c11a0caec","tid":763744,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"睇情況"},{"pid":"cafdf4efc2b878f35b830b5c00ceb83bbde4e295","tid":763744,"uid":164913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d882160e243c3151ccb9b1da29ad604b4ba294f","tid":763744,"uid":60171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:27:28.000Z","msg":"我係唔可以屈服於呢個反智行為上.jpg"},{"pid":"91d515ab7593b07bddbbdc2b6a19cc1cd7a0c607","tid":763744,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cbfa036203171b40a60b58eb87c42919faf4952","tid":763744,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"守同唔守規矩之間既空間好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958b0e3ebbd93cc2bbd01020b470780ba84265e5","tid":763744,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"規則由你定，咁就係好事!<br />\n其他規則就睇心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d68d9ce175ee8ddd75b00bac721ce37a9d0bee","tid":763744,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"壞事,所以我發唔到達同埋俾人笑on9"},{"pid":"6cf44c357f1a1ba80c3cbb979c06c4c17148adb9","tid":763744,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"做正確的事 唔做錯事<br />\n咩係正確咩係錯自己思考下"},{"pid":"de84414759218d8b7a5dfeae96eac113c9453030","tid":763744,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"守則係死人係生<br />\n有好多野係比左一個概念令你去遵守<br />\n但唔係盲目"},{"pid":"718a068ad70ae00e10ac655a398775f92fa51b23","tid":763744,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"又開 d 兩個極端 post"},{"pid":"a1b87fc9a17d4b204b288b229c9af62a0cb7bc97","tid":763744,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8d68d9ce175ee8ddd75b00bac721ce37a9d0bee","tid":763744,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"壞事,所以我發唔到達同埋俾人笑on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"有時太守規矩的確賺唔到大錢，因為通常賺太錢嘅人某程度上係注視喺灰色地帶<br />\n但係如果你守規矩又賺到大錢，就可以站喺不敗之地同道德高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ff7110cd7f13428890fc9c5aa796ff7a648c29","tid":763744,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"依個世界除物理法則之外<br />\n<br />\n全部規矩都係人為，要睇清係既得利益者自利而定，定真係為公眾好而定既<br />\n<br />\n後者可以守。<br />\n<br />\n前者有可能的話盡量無視。"},{"pid":"416bcb1c4f455c26a8529edf8fa8a06526316d24","tid":763744,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"規矩係人定<br />\n背後代表咗一套思想<br />\n你認同就跟，唔認同嘅話就睇後果<br />\n<br />\n每個人都有原則<br />\n只有依照原則而行而達成嘅目的先有意義"}]}